{"tid":457263,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣同個女仔拉返近個距離","createTime":"2017-11-03T16:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T09:04:21.000Z","uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a5af5e76cca335eeb3952d5bdcd6ddf3afa6e205","tid":457263,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"前排識咗個女仔<br />\n傾咗個幾星期都幾啱傾<br />\n但前幾日佢聽人講啲關於我嘅事<br />\n話我雙面人個啲<br />\n之後就開始驚我<br />\n前兩日冇主動搵我<br />\n今日問佢個fd，話佢仲係驚我咁樣，又話佢只係想相處了解下(好老實講我都覺太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n係今日我打蛇隨棍上聊咗佢幾句<br />\n佢冇之前咁hea，又會自己搵話題<br />\n但講嘢始終冇一開始咁close<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打講下可以點樣慢慢拉返近啲個距離等我參考下"},{"pid":"1ed57737bd6a4c21bb8ddb1d1aae703c30bd8648","tid":457263,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea8c1d57e9de075199503b716248f7752a543913","tid":457263,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇</blockquote><br />\n大波小爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7431ffa5fde171e181d0277eb1f07c7dfed9268b","tid":457263,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽人講兩句就話驚咗你，笑出聲"},{"pid":"40ec83590ce0cb3d36577c1441c878cbbb775c82","tid":457263,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"邀請佢共渡纏綿既一晚"},{"pid":"d08b893d261f7601aadb41167587d2b99a1f99ef","tid":457263,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽人講兩句就話驚咗你，笑出聲</blockquote><br />\n有冇咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1910d25ca5392a33c63d6b08baeb274a6c7